wikipedia_page.main: Jess Greenberg (born 20 December 1994) is an English YouTube personality, singer, and acoustic guitarist from London, England.

response: Other artists that covered this song include Hinder, Etta James, Link Wray, Slade, The Cult, INXS, Ozzy Osbourne with Miss Piggy, Bruce Springsteen, Slayer, Blue Öyster Cult, Status Quo, Fanfare Ciocărlia, Krokus, Wilson Pickett, La Renga and Jess Greenberg.
